je niet en schrikken gevoelige katten niet af.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-28 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-pair-it-with-the-App-x5.webp?v=1746770974&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-pair-it-with-the-App-x5.webp?v=1746770974&width=1250'\n          alt='Popur X5 kan aan een app worden gekoppeld voor extra controle'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-28 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-pair-it-with-the-App-x5.webp?v=1746770974&width=1250'\n            alt='Popur X5 kan aan een app worden gekoppeld voor extra controle'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs text-white/70'>Koppel desgewenst met de app om gebruik te volgen en instellingen aan te passen zonder bij de bak te staan.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n\n      <figure class='flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/80'>\n        <img\n          class='lazyload h-28 w-full object-cover'\n          src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-move-around-easily-with-casters-x5.webp?v=1746770979&width=416'\n          data-src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-move-around-easily-with-casters-x5.webp?v=1746770979&width=1250'\n          alt='Popur X5 heeft wieltjes om makkelijk te verplaatsen'\n        />\n        <noscript>\n          <img\n            class='h-28 w-full object-cover'\n            src='https://popur.com/cdn/shop/files/More-features-move-around-easily-with-casters-x5.webp?v=1746770979&width=1250'\n            alt='Popur X5 heeft wieltjes om makkelijk te verplaatsen'\n          />\n        </noscript>\n        <figcaption class='flex-1 px-4 pb-4 pt-3 text-xs t